<style>
    .promote-menu {margin-top: 30px;}
    .promote-share {line-height:40px;padding:30px;border:3px solid #f2e7d6;background-color: #fffdd7;}
    .promote-share label {color:#666;font-size:14px;font-weight:100;float: left; width: 120px;padding-right: 18px;text-align: right;}
    .promote-share .link{width: 350px;margin: 0 0 0 138px;padding: 0 10px;color:#333;border: 1px solid #eaeaea;background-color: #fff;}
    .promote-share .copy{float:right;margin-right:80px;display:inline-block;width:120px;font-size:12px;height: 40px;border: 1px solid #E0322D;color: #fff;background-color:#e30a20;display: block;text-align: center;line-height: 40px;cursor:pointer;}
    .promote-share .bdsharebuttonbox {position:relative;top: 6px;}
    .promote-box {padding-bottom: 50px;}

    .promote-box .total {padding-left:10px;border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6e6;}
    .promote-box .tb {width: 50%;}
    .promote-box .tb td {padding: 30px 0;color:#999;}
    .promote-box .tb strong {display: block;font-size: 30px;margin-top: 10px;color:#333;}

    .promote-total {padding: 10px 20px;border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6e6;}
    .promote-total .btn-exchange {float:right;margin:22px 20px 0 0;display:inline-block;width:70px;height:30px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#E0322D;border:1px solid #E0322D;display:block;text-align:center;line-height:28px;border-radius:2px;}
    .promote-total .tb{width: 100%;}
    .promote-total .tb td {padding: 20px 0;color:#999;}
    .promote-total .tb em {display: block;font-size: 30px;margin-top: 10px;color:#333;}
    .promote-total .tb em span{font-size: 20px;}
    .promote-total .tb strong {font-weight:100;display: block;font-size: 16px;margin-top: 10px;color:#333;}
    .promote-step {padding: 30px 0;text-align: center;}
    .promote-intro {line-height: 26px;}
    .promote-intro h5 {font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px;font-weight: 700;}
    .promote-intro li {margin-top: 40px;}
    .promote-intro .count {font-size: 14px;font-weight: 700;}
    .promote-intro .count em {font-size: 30px;color:#a40000;}
</style>
<script>
    /* bd_share */
    window._bd_share_config = {
        common : {
            bdText : '来牛金网炒股，开户快，收益高',
            bdDesc : '来牛金网炒股，开户快，收益高',
            bdUrl : '',
            bdPic : 'http://www.niujinwang.com/images/logo100.jpg'
        },
        share : [{
            "bdSize" : 16
        }]
    };
    with(document)0[(getElementsByTagName('head')[0]||body).appendChild(createElement('script')).src='/js/bd_share.js'];
    $("#J_copy").zclip({
        path: "/images/ZeroClipboard.swf",
        copy: function () {
            return $("#J_link").text();
        },
        afterCopy: function() {
            alert('您的推广码已经复制到剪贴板');
        }
    });
    $("#J_copy2").zclip({
        path: "/images/ZeroClipboard.swf",
        copy: function () {
            return $("#J_link2").text();
        },
        afterCopy: function() {
            alert('您的推广链接已经复制到剪贴板');
        }
    });
</script>
<div class="fl tra_right">
    <div class="neword_menu promote-menu">
        <div class="neword_menulist jq_menuList">
            <ul>
                <li ng-class="{selected: vm.showFirstPage}" ng-click="vm.showFirstPage = true">推广详情</li>
                <li ng-class="{selected: !vm.showFirstPage}" ng-click="vm.showFirstPage = false">我的用户</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--#推广详情-->
    <div class="promote-box" ng-show="vm.showFirstPage">
        <div class="promote-step">
            <img src="/images/promote-step.jpg" width="741" height="21" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="promote-share">
            <div class="url" style="margin-bottom: 10px">
                <a class="copy" id="J_copy2">复制邀请码</a>
                <label>您的邀请码</label>
                <div class="link" id="J_link2">\{{vm.referName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="url">
                <a class="copy" id="J_copy">复制链接</a>
                <label>您的推广链接</label>
                <div class="link" id="J_link">http://www.niujinwang.com/?refer=\{{vm.user.referName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="btns">
                <label>分享您的推广链接</label>
                <div class="bdsharebuttonbox" data-tag="share_1">
                    <a class="bds_qzone" data-cmd="qzone" href="#"></a>
                    <a class="bds_tsina" data-cmd="tsina"></a>
                    <a class="bds_baidu" data-cmd="baidu"></a>
                    <a class="bds_renren" data-cmd="renren"></a>
                    <a class="bds_tqq" data-cmd="tqq"></a>
                    <a class="bds_weixin" data-cmd="weixin"></a>
                    <a class="bds_more" data-cmd="more"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="promote-intro">
            <li>
                <h5>如何推广？</h5>
                <p>牛金网推广是一种按用户融资赚取佣金的模式，您可以通过朋友、QQ、微信、微博、博客、论坛或在自己的网站上进行推广，所有通过您的推广链接访问过来的用户，注册后都将成为您的下线用户，而当这些用户在本站融资时，您就可以最高赚取7%的佣金。</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h5>佣金怎么结算？</h5>
                <p>您的用户在注册后一年内每发生一笔融资，在融资完成后，您即可获得一笔佣金，当您的佣金达到100元的时候，即可兑换取出，也可以在本站进行融资。</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h5>推广佣金收入计算</h5>
                <p>推广获得用户后您的用户开始融资，100个用户人均8倍杠杆融资10万元使用22天(1月)；</p>
            </li>
            <li class="count">
                <p>100人×10万元＝1000万元融资</p>
                <p>1000万*22天*19.9元=437,800元融资管理费</p>
                <p>437,800元融资管理费×7%＝月最高赚佣金3万元 合计年收益<em>36</em>万元</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div><!--/推广详情-->
    <!--#我的用户-->
    <div class="promote-box" ng-hide="vm.showFirstPage">
        <div class="promote-total">
            <table class="tb">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        当前佣金
                        <a href="" class="btn-exchange" ng-click="vm.transMoney()">兑换</a>
